high_descs: grab the clear bowl off of the kitchen island
take the bowl over to the fridge
place the bowl inside of the fridge to cool, then take it back out
bring the cooled bowl over to the kitchen counter right of the sink
put it in the cabinet below the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: put a cooled bowl away in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Go to the kitchen island behind you.
Take the transparent bowl to the left of the kettle.
Bring the bowl to the fridge in front of you.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Take the bowl out of the fridge.
Place the bowl in the cabinet to your left.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go the kitchen island on the side with the oven.
Pick up the square container that is behind the spatula.
Go around the island and to the refrigerator.
Place the container on the middle shelf of the refrigerator and leave it in there for seven seconds before taking it back out.
Turn left and face the lower cabinets on the right of the sink.
Open the rightmost cabinet and place the container inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled square container in a cabinet.
